  "t1"."" "d1",
  SUM("t1"."") "m0",
  SUM("t1"."") "m1"
FROM "" "t1"
INNER JOIN "" "t2" ON ("t1"."" = "t2"."")
GROUP BY "t1"."_ID",
  "t1".""
FETCH FIRST 20000 ROWS ONLY
